{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"X9i6HckFgvkUQ0jaz25Gj","title":"Lessons","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[],"anchors":{"language-schools":{"type":"header","value":"language-schools","line":9,"column":0},"live-the-language":{"type":"header","value":"live-the-language","line":20,"column":0},"08082021":{"type":"header","value":"08082021","line":37,"column":0},"hsk-hànyǔ-shuǐpíng-kǎoshì---chinese-proficiency-test":{"type":"header","value":"hsk-hànyǔ-shuǐpíng-kǎoshì---chinese-proficiency-test","line":41,"column":0}},"fname":"lessons","updated":1633192928533,"created":1630837564983,"parent":"tP0mD90vo9yAk1VHyoVSk","children":["ZBY8LRw9QwooZsMY4Kq9T"],"data":{},"contentHash":"394a6668e9e20636818128bce5444e18","custom":{},"schema":{"schemaId":"lessons","moduleId":"lessons"}},"body":"<h1 id=\"lessons\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#lessons\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Lessons</h1>\n<h2 id=\"language-schools\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#language-schools\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Language Schools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thatsmandarin.com/1-on-1-courses/?gclid=EAIaIQobChMIppqj4M7n8gIV-Z1LBR0MiAJWEAAYASAAEgLbR_D_BwE\">That's Mandarin</a>\n<ul>\n<li>192 RMB / class</li>\n<li>Dongzhimen Campus (about 7 km one way)<a href=\"https://www.google.com.sg/maps/dir/39.8974526,116.4700371/7+Xinzhong+St,+Dongcheng+Qu,+Beijing+Shi,+China,+100006/@39.9147514,116.4484899,14z/data=!4m9!4m8!1m0!1m5!1m1!1s0x35f1acbf42b95cef:0xf31a0c6f564ac14b!2m2!1d116.438497!2d39.938764!3e2\">Map</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ltl-beijing.com/chinese-tutor-beijing/\">Live the Language</a>\n<ul>\n<li>177 RMB / class (less if you buy more upfront)</li>\n<li>Jianguo Rd. 88, Xiandai SOHO, Building B, 504</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://beijing.universitytutor.com/beijing_mandarin-chinese-tutoring\">Beijing University Tutor</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"live-the-language\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#live-the-language\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Live the Language</h3>\n<p>Potential Schedule 2 Times a Week\nMonday? Thursday? 1.5 hours each</p>\n<p>Questions: Assessment?</p>\n<p>Goals:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Being able to understand daily conversation (not news level)</li>\n<li>Being able to do basic engagements - Restaurant; Didi; </li>\n<li>Being able to engage in a conversation with friends</li>\n<li>Basic Reading - Food Menus / WeChat / Alipay / Meituan / TaoBao</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Non Goals:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Business</li>\n<li>Learning to Write</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"08082021\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#08082021\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>08.08.2021</h4>\n<p>Chat with Maria - estimates I'm at HKS 3-4? Says I should be able to get to 4-5.  Had a 5 minute conversation in Mandarin!</p>\n<h2 id=\"hsk-hànyǔ-shuǐpíng-kǎoshì---chinese-proficiency-test\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#hsk-hànyǔ-shuǐpíng-kǎoshì---chinese-proficiency-test\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>HSK (Hànyǔ Shuǐpíng Kǎoshì) - Chinese Proficiency Test</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>HSK 1 - 150 new words</li>\n<li>HSK 2 - 150 </li>\n<li>HSK 3 - 300 words total</li>\n<li>HSK 4 - 600 words total </li>\n<li>HSK 5 - 1300 new words</li>\n<li>HSK 6 - 2500 new words</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Most grammar (yǔfǎ) is complete by the end of HSK 3.It's a big step up from 3 -> 4 </p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"children\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#children\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Children</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/ZBY8LRw9QwooZsMY4Kq9T\">2021</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"tP0mD90vo9yAk1VHyoVSk","title":"Journey in 中文","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[],"anchors":{},"fname":"root","updated":1633192679985,"created":1632988446599,"parent":null,"children":["H9qDzxUwhOmeT4zlcaKbf","VGTsTXhrREuYjcjspAW6g","X9i6HckFgvkUQ0jaz25Gj","tSyiuG6PVRvuDxGxvYhxA","YXK3064rlQB4yQa8iOpYT"],"data":{},"contentHash":"c115f61742eba4eb575e0b4166d6a0c6","custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"body":"\nIn this journal, I document my journey in trying to learn Chinese for the 2nd time.\n\nMost of the notes will be from my language classes. Some notes are also arranged as references, for example with grammar and useful vocabulary. But in an effort to practice writing, I will also try to write some notes in Chinese about my experiences here in Beijing.\n\nThe grammar may be poor and the sentences simple, please bear with me. Starting simple is part of the learning experience; hopefully with time the posts will become more interesting!\n\n谢谢！"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":1,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"useFMTitle":true,"useNoteTitleForLink":true,"noAutoCreateOnDefinition":true,"noLegacyNoteRef":true,"noXVaultWikiLink":true,"lookupConfirmVaultOnCreate":false,"mermaid":true,"useKatex":true,"autoFoldFrontmatter":true,"usePrettyRefs":true,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"lookup":{"note":{"selectionType":"selectionExtract"}},"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain","firstDayOfWeek":1},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"site":{"copyAssets":true,"siteHierarchies":["root"],"siteRootDir":"docs","usePrettyRefs":true,"title":"Jonathan's 中文 Journal","description":"My Journal for Learning Mandarin","siteLastModified":true,"gh_edit_branch":"main","duplicateNoteBehavior":{"action":"useVault","payload":["vault"]},"siteUrl":"https://jonathanyeung.github.io/","usePrettyLinks":true,"siteNotesDir":"notes","siteFaviconPath":"favicon.ico","gh_edit_link":true,"gh_edit_link_text":"Edit this page on GitHub","gh_root":"docs/","gh_edit_view_mode":"edit","writeStubs":true,"siteIndex":"root"},"initializeRemoteVaults":true}},"__N_SSG":true}